com.netflix.spectator.ipc

Class ServerGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.netflix.spectator.ipc.ServerGroup

  • public class ServerGroup
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper for parsing Netflix server group names that follow the Frigga conventions. For more information see the IEP documentation for server groups.

    Frigga is not used for the actual parsing as it is quite inefficient. See the ServerGroupParsing benchmark for a comparison.
